{"tid":1649334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港黑衣少女中英街拍攝　一度被公安帶走","createTime":"2019-10-12T15:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T11:58:59.000Z","uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6c8355d6389e95518557bb2c2a83cd5b4db13a71","tid":1649334,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:16:49.000Z","msg":"一名香港黑衣少女昨日（11日）手持攝錄器材進入沙頭角中英街內拍攝，<span style=\"color: red;\">被指身上的黑衣有「港獨」字句，被邊防武警及公安帶返派出所</span>，幸經訓示「教育」後獲放行。<br />\n<br />\n從網民片段及貼文所見，事發昨早約11時，據稱家住沙頭角、就讀粉嶺一中學的香港女生，與母親到中英街，當時她身穿黑T恤黑短褲，腳踏拖鞋，拿着一個三腳架連攝影機，經過關口進入中國邊境時，<span style=\"color: red;\">有民眾指她所穿黑衣印有港獨字眼，懷疑她過境示威，並通知公安人員</span>。<br />\n<br />\n邊防武警及公安人員到場截獲女生，有人聲稱欲到中英街拍攝，但未有提及拍攝內容，執法人員遂要求她到沙頭角派出所接受調查，據悉其母本在港界等候，其後聞訊亦往陪同女兒。女生接受訓示後獲釋放，與母親返港。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191012/s00001/1570892812624/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191012%2Fs00001%2F1570892812624%2F&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9jMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=7965a0ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191012%2Fs00001%2F1570892812624%2F&h=f3017b16\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191012/s00001/1570892812624/</a>"},{"pid":"df1f6417f82008e68764cd62ee0366bbb3c2a6f8","tid":1649334,"uid":53592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c86feaa1326b99a315a290e03c05441b2912e8a","tid":1649334,"uid":2949,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:19:12.000Z","msg":"「教育」<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806a54a0d48c537817993978883b2a06d0f587ab","tid":1649334,"uid":236368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"正常人唔會係香港過到唐界架喎<br />\n<br />\n好大機會本身